Data availability

            Raw shotgun metagenomic sequences are available in the NCBI Sequence Read Archive (BioProject accession no. PRJNA1434723). Raw 16S rRNA amplicon sequences from antibiotic-containing plates are available in the NCBI Sequence Read Archive (BioProject accession no. PRJNA533082). CARD is available at https://card.mcmaster.ca/download, whereas the Resfams core database is available at https://www.dantaslab.org/resfams. The metagenome- and GeoChip-based ARG abundance tables, assembled strain genomes, soil physical and chemical attributes, and plant biomass and richness are available at https://doi.org/10.6084/m9.figshare.28829036. Source data are provided with this paper.
          Code availability

            Scripts on the metagenomic data processing and statistical analyses are available at https://github.com/Linwei-Wu/warming_soil_resistome.
